@startuml
' The monotonic mailbox receipt lifecycle: a read implies delivered, an ack implies
' read + delivered (COALESCE, never moving a timestamp backward). Palette: mailbox=cyan.
skinparam backgroundColor transparent
skinparam defaultFontName Inter
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #cffafe
  BorderColor #0e7490
  FontColor #164e63
}

[*] --> Sent : a2a_send_message
Sent --> Delivered : push channel\nOR inbox pull
Delivered : delivered_at stamped
Delivered --> Read : agent reads it
Read : read_at  (implies delivered_at)
Read --> Acked : a2a_ack_message
Acked : acked_at  (implies read_at + delivered_at)
Acked --> [*]
Read --> Replied : a2a_reply_message
Replied : new message, reply_to → this id
Replied --> [*]

note right of Sent
  3 addressing dimensions:
  to_session · to_project_id · to_agent
end note
@enduml
